<%# app/views/alert_mailer/new_jobs_found.text.erb %>
Hi there,

We found <%= @jobs.count %> new job(s) matching your alert for: "<%= @alert.query %>"

---

<% @jobs.each do |job| %>
<%= job.title %> at <%= job.company.name %>
<%= job.description %>
---
<% end %>

To stop receiving these alerts, visit this URL:
<%= unsubscribe_alert_url(@alert.signed_id(purpose: :unsubscribe)) %>